     1‚Üí# The serve command ‚Ä¶
    27‚Üí### Server options
    29‚ÜíThe `serve` hostname defaults to `localhost`, and the port defaults to `3000`. Either option can be specified on the command line:
    30‚Üí
    31‚Üí```bash
    32‚Üímdbook serve path/to/book -p 8000 -n 127.0.0.1 
    33‚Üí```
